OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F163A1781621296
OL,1,Wj5hw1~{4k7juhw1{$             G2/2
OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wed 1 Jul to Wed 15 Jul
OL,6,FHigh pressure patterns are slightly
OL,7,Fmore likely than low pressure patterns
OL,8,Fduring this period, meaning settled
OL,9,Fand drier than average conditions are
OL,10,Fmost probable. However, there is still
OL,11,Fa chance of some changeable, more
OL,12,Funsettled conditions could develop at
OL,13,Ftimes. Temperatures are likely to be
OL,14,Fabove normal, with a greater than
OL,15,Fnormal chance of hot conditions
OL,16,Fdeveloping.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
